title: Come Back... Be Here (Taylor's Version)
description:
Ana says that Taylor Swift writes the soundtrack to her life.. and this song once again proves it! Come back, be here is about the complicated feelings involved when you can't be around the one you love because of work and distance getting in the way. There are lots of theories about the inspiration behind this song... We break it all down!
What did we miss? What else would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us, and we love hearing from you!
